      { q: `How do I find a moving company for my Seattle move?`, a: `Look for a Washington State licensed mover (check the UTC license database), read Google and Yelp reviews, get at least 3 quotes, and confirm the company carries liability insurance. On The Go Moving is licensed (HG-064180), insured, and has served the Seattle/Eastside area since 2007.` }
