      { q: `What should I do to prepare for residential movers?`, a: `To prepare for movers: pack everything in labeled boxes before they arrive (unless you've hired packing services), disassemble large furniture if possible, clear pathways through your home, reserve parking for the moving truck, separate items you'll transport yourself (valuables, plants, medications), and have payment ready in the agreed form.` }
