      { type: "h2", heading: `What to Know About Living in Bellevue, WA`, body: `Here are some valuable tips for moving to Bellevue before you go. The climate is agreeable, with comparatively mild winters and short warm summers. Enjoy a vibrant community with plenty of jobs and businesses, quality housing, reliable transport, and excellent schools.` },
      { type: "h3", heading: `Registering Your Car`, body: `Ensure you have your Certificate of Ownership (Title), proof of identity, payment for taxes, and proof of emissions inspection (if applicable). Bellevue School District is a top-rated public school district, serving over 21,000 students (Grades PK-12). 79% of its students are proficient in reading, and at least 73% proficient in math. While the number of jobs in Bellevue has fluctuated since 2000, there has been an upward trend. The average annual growth rate of jobs is 1.12%. A family of four will spend around $4,238 per month. On average, a single person’s expenses are $1,100 (without...` },
      { type: "h3", heading: `Moving Resource s`, body: `Bellevue has plenty of resources for short and long-distance moves, including On The Go.` },
      { type: "h3", heading: `Culture and Contemporary Life`, body: `There are dozens of museums and galleries in the area, plus tons of restaurants serving everything from classic American fare to excellent sushi!` },
      { type: "h2", heading: `Moving to Bellevue, WA: On The Go Moving`, body: `There's so much in Bellevue, WA, that can enhance your life, and On the Go Moving will help ensure your move to this vibrant city goes as smoothly as possible. We'll do everything from packing up your belongings to ensuring they arrive safely at their new home in Bellevue. If you're moving to Bellevue , WA, or nearby areas, get in touch with On The Go Moving today. Call (425) 440-3241 or contact us online for a free estimate. How to Keep Your Identity Safe When Moving to Bellevue Most people don’t think about securing their identity when they’re moving. Surprisingly, more than 12… How to Keep...` }
